A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Howard County – Speed Monitoring Systems – Authorization
3 Ho. Co. 9–25
4 FOR the purpose of expanding the authorization to place and use speed monitoring systems
5 on highways in Howard County; requiring the fines collected by Howard County as
6 a result of violations enforced by certain speed monitoring systems to be used for
7 public safety purposes, including pedestrian or highway safety programs, or to fund
8 deferred maintenance work at Howard County public schools; and generally relating
9 to the placement and use of a speed monitoring system in Howard County.
